# SPA fallback — route every unmatched URL back to index.html so React
# Router can take over on the client. Without this, hard-refreshing
# /login (or any other client-side route) returns the host's default 404
# because no file exists at that path.
#
# Honored by Netlify, Render static sites, and Cloudflare Pages. Vercel
# uses vercel.json (also in this repo). Other hosts: configure the
# equivalent rewrite rule.
/*    /index.html   200
